Shehu, younger brother of Kebbi Governor Atiku Bagudu, is dead. Special Adviser to the Governor on Media Yahaya Sarki, announced this in a statement. He said the 55-year-old died on Tuesday evening at a private hospital in Abuja after a brief illness. Funeral prayer will take place on Wednesday, March 3, 2021at the National Mosque, Abuja, by 11: 00 am, according to him.